entries.title_d: Go make your presence known at the Witchblood Clan burial grounds to occupy them while Hutt forces infiltrate their stronghold
entries.title: Dathomir System: Provide a distraction at the Witchblood Clan Burial Grounds
entries.quest_reachpoint_d: Travel to this location to begin the operation
entries.quest_location_d: The spaceborne burial ground of the Dathomir Witchblood Clan
entries.quest_defendpoint_d: Stay at this location until you are given instruction to leave
entries.outofrange_failed: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast1 You went too far from the burial zone! Witchblood scouts are returning to their base. The mission is scrapped! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.outofrange: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast1 Get back to the pirates' burial zone! If the Witchblood disengage, they'll find us and the mission will be lost! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.mission_complete: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast1 Great work! We've set all the detonators at their stronghold. We're clearing out so we can set off the charges.  Meet us back at Jabba's Palace \#pcontrast3 >
entries.found_loc: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast1 Fly to that location and keep the Witchblood clan busy. We'll sneak into their hidden base, and set detonators! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.first_attack: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast3 All right! Here they come! Keep them busy while we work our way into their base... \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast1 Stay focused, and stay alive.  We need them focused on you and not us. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast3 Hyperspace signatures detected in close proximity. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_loc: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast1 Okay! You've entered the Witchblood clan's sacred burial zone... they're sure to descend on you shortly.  I wouldn't want to be you right now. \#pcontrast3 >
